OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FUS singer D4vd has been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder after the dismembered body of a
OL,8,Fmissing 14-year-old girl was found in
OL,9,Fhis car last year.
OL,11,FD4vd, real name David Burke, 21, has
OL,12,Fbeen charged with first-degree murder,
OL,13,Flewd and lascivious acts with an
OL,14,Findividual under 14, and mutilating a
OL,15,Fbody in the killing of Celeste Rivas
OL,16,FHernandez.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
