OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776753489
OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FRivas Hernandez was reported missing
OL,7,Fby her family from her home in Lake
OL,8,FElsinore, about 70 miles southeast of
OL,9,FLos Angeles, in 2024, when she was 13,
OL,10,Fbut authorities say she was 14 when
OL,11,Fshe died.
OL,13,FHer decomposed body was found in an
OL,14,Fabandoned Tesla belonging to D4vd,
OL,15,Ftowed from the Hollywood Hills on
OL,16,FSeptember 8, the day after she would
OL,17,Fhave turned 15.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
