OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAttorneys for D4vd, a Houston-born alt-
OL,12,Fpop singer, protested his innocence in
OL,13,Fa statement released after homicide
OL,14,Fdetectives arrested him on Thursday at
OL,15,Fa home in Hollywood.
OL,17,F"Let us be clear - the actual evidence
OL,18,Fin this case will show that David
OL,19,FBurke did not murder Celeste Rivas
OL,20,FHernandez and he was not the cause of
OL,21,Fher death," the lawyers said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
