OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FThe murder charges include special
OL,7,Fcircumstances - such as lying in wait,
OL,8,Fcommitting a crime for financial gain
OL,9,Fand murdering the witness in an
OL,10,Finvestigation - that could carry the
OL,11,Fdeath penalty.
OL,13,FIt is unclear whether prosecutors will
OL,14,Fseek such measures.
OL,16,FD4vd had been under investigation by
OL,17,Fan LA County grand jury looking into
OL,18,FRivas Hernandez's death, which was
OL,19,Frevealed in February when his mother,
OL,20,Ffather and brother objected to
OL,21,Fsubpoenas demanding they testify.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
