OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776753489
OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FThe singer's 2023 Tesla Model Y had
OL,7,Fbeen towed from an upscale Hollywood
OL,8,FHills neighbourhood where it had been
OL,9,Fapparently abandoned, when Rivas
OL,10,FHernandez's dismembered body was found
OL,11,Fin a series of bags inside it.
OL,13,FNo cause of death has been publicly
OL,14,Frevealed, and police got a judge to
OL,15,Fblock the release of details of the
OL,16,Fautopsy.
OL,18,FD4vd continued his North American tour
OL,19,Fafter the immediate discovery, but
OL,20,Flater cancelled the final two shows
OL,21,Fand a European tour that was to follow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
