OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FRivas Hernandez's family have largely
OL,7,Fstayed out of public view since her
OL,8,Fbody was discovered.
OL,10,F"The Rivas Hernandez family is
OL,11,Fcommitted to ensuring that Celeste's
OL,12,Fvoice is heard and her memory is
OL,13,Fhonoured throughout this process,"
OL,14,FPatrick Steinfeld, their attorney,
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
