OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1776753489
OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FConnections between Rivas Hernandez
OL,7,Fand D4vd surfaced before she was
OL,8,Freported missing, with the two
OL,9,Fappearing together in a livestream on
OL,10,FTwitch in January 2024, ITV News' US
OL,11,Fpartner, CNN, reports.
OL,13,FBetween January and March 2024, the
OL,14,Fsinger was photographed stepping out
OL,15,Fof a Tesla close to her home, with the
OL,16,Fimages shared online.
OL,18,FCNN geolocated and chronolocated the
OL,19,Fphotos to verify when and where they
OL,20,Fwere taken.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
