OL,3,CSinger D4vd charged with murdering
OL,4,Cmissing girl, 14, found in his car
OL,6,FD4vd, pronounced "David", gained
OL,7,Fpopularity among Gen Z for his blend
OL,8,Fof indie rock, R&B and lo-fi pop, and
OL,9,Fwent viral on TikTok in 2022 with the
OL,10,Fhit Romantic Homicide, which peaked at
OL,11,FNo. 4 on Billboard's Hot Rock and
OL,12,FAlternative Songs chart.
OL,14,FHe signed with Darkroom and Interscope
OL,15,FRecords and released his debut EP,
OL,16,FPetals to Thorns, and a follow-up, The
OL,17,FLost Petals, in 2023.
